26
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,110
You're right.

27
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:33,790
But I think that we have no clues at all,

28
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:36,240
and we have no idea where to start looking for Shaoyi.

29
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:38,000
Since Mr. Guo seems suspicious,

30
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,900
let's keep investigating him.

31
