[Gold and Silver Jewelry]

48
00:03:44,740 --> 00:03:46,620
[Gold and Silver Jewelry]

49
00:03:45,010 --> 00:03:46,740
Greetings, Young Master Duan.

50
00:03:47,540 --> 00:03:49,210
Are you masochists?

51
00:03:49,310 --> 00:03:50,630
After getting beaten up,

52
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:52,030
you've become so polite.

53
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:56,700
Where is your boss?

54
00:03:57,470 --> 00:04:00,590
Young Master Duan, what can I do for you?

55
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:02,550
I want to ask why you

56
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:03,870
went to the academy to see Mr. Guo today.

57
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:04,990
Since Young Master Duan asks,

58
00:04:04,990 --> 00:04:07,440
I'll tell you everything I know.

59
00:04:07,510 --> 00:04:08,630
I'll explain everything to you

60
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:11,270
honestly, reliably

61
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:11,970
and truthfully...

62
00:04:11,970 --> 00:04:13,410
Enough. Enough.

63
00:04:14,230 --> 00:04:16,800
Please answer the question briefly.

64
00:04:16,950 --> 00:04:19,880
Mr. Guo is a regular customer here.

65
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,550
He owes me a lot of money.

66
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,190
So I went personally

67
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,510
to collect the debts.

68
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:27,830
Did he and Shaoyi have any contact at the casino?

69
00:04:27,970 --> 00:04:29,370
As far as I know,

70
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,640
they didn't have any contact.

71
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:34,700
Young Master Shaoyi is a student at the Jizhou Academy.

72
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:37,670
If his teacher found out he came to a place like this,

73
00:04:38,710 --> 00:04:39,970
he'd be in big trouble.

74
00:04:40,030 --> 00:04:41,830
Mr. Guo cares about his reputation.

75
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:44,310
Every time he comes here, he avoids people.

76
00:04:44,790 --> 00:04:48,430
So they probably didn't have any contact.

77
00:04:50,630 --> 00:04:52,430
This clue has led nowhere again.

78
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:54,909
Young Master Duan, don't worry.

79
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:56,400
I know many people

80
00:04:56,450 --> 00:04:58,990
from all walks of life.

81
00:04:59,350 --> 00:05:01,680
Your business is my business.

82
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,650
Don't worry.

83
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:05,110
I'll keep looking.

84
00:05:05,990 --> 00:05:06,870
Thank you.

85
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:10,070
The Duan family of Changqing will remember your kindness.

86
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:11,280
I'm flattered.

87
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:12,510
It's my duty.

88
00:05:12,510 --> 00:05:13,310
It's my duty.

89
00:05:21,310 --> 00:05:23,110
Why is this thing glowing?

90
00:05:23,190 --> 00:05:24,590
This is a luminous pearl.

91
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:27,270
Where did you get it?

92
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:28,080
Mr. Guo.

93
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,930
It's collateral for his debts.

94
00:05:30,150 --> 00:05:31,610
I had someone appraise it.

95
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:34,470
It's worth 3,000 taels of silver.

96
00:05:52,270 --> 00:05:53,470
You finally came.

97
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:57,720
You've been threatening me.

98
00:05:57,830 --> 00:05:58,960
How could I not come?

99
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,000
Where's my money?

100
00:06:00,150 --> 00:06:01,200
Where is the luminous pearl?

101
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:03,530
Why would I carry the luminous pearl on me?

102
00:06:03,910 --> 00:06:05,630
What if you turn your back on me,

103
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:07,920
and kill me like you did to Duan Shaoyi?

104
00:06:08,990 --> 00:06:09,720
Don't worry.

105
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,700
I've put the luminous pearl

106
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:12,100
in a very suitable place.

107
00:06:13,030 --> 00:06:14,110
If anything happens to me,

108
00:06:14,110 --> 00:06:16,280
someone will take out the luminous pearl

109
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,940
to prove you're the murderer.

110
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:22,030
So I advise you to give me the money obediently.

111
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:25,110
Once I get the money, I'll keep my mouth shut,

112
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:27,520
and won't reveal anything

113
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:29,040
I saw that night.

114
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,909
[Propitious Winds and Rains]

115
00:06:47,380 --> 00:06:48,760
You told everyone

116
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:52,560
that you returned to the academy after Duan Shaoyi disappeared.

117
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:55,050
But I clearly saw you

118
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:57,120
leave the academy the night before.

119
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:02,530
The luminous pearl

120
00:07:03,540 --> 00:07:06,270
is the best evidence that you killed Duan Shaoyi.

121
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,510
Cheng Mufei,

122
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:11,220
do you want the Duan family of Changqing to know

123
00:07:11,650 --> 00:07:13,310
that the Principal they trust

124
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,430
is actually a murderer?

125
00:07:15,470 --> 00:07:16,780
I did not kill Duan Shaoyi!

126
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:18,040
You might convince me,

127
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:20,150
but can you convince Duan Yu?

128
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:21,710
If he finds out,

129
00:07:21,990 --> 00:07:24,120
he'll definitely avenge Duan Shaoyi.

130
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:26,160
I will explain to Duan Yu myself.

131
00:07:27,670 --> 00:07:28,740
Don't lie.

132
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,200
If you dared to explain,

133
00:07:31,790 --> 00:07:34,310
why did you use your wife's tuberculosis as an excuse

134
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,720
to avoid meeting Duan Yu?

135
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:38,190
Aren't you afraid that they'll find out

136
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:41,909
your wife doesn't have tuberculosis?

137
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:43,790
All this

138
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:47,230
is just a lie from you.

139
00:07:47,350 --> 00:07:48,040
Shut up!

140
00:08:06,180 --> 00:08:07,870
Sacred Blood Sect.

141
00:08:12,030 --> 00:08:13,030
Principal Cheng.

142
00:08:13,590 --> 00:08:16,010
The dead Mr. Guo

143
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,640
is a gift from me to you.

144
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:20,150
I've helped you eliminate a future problem.

145
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:22,920
Shouldn't you thank me first?

146
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:23,940
Ridiculous.

147
00:08:24,150 --> 00:08:25,830
Why should I thank you?

148
00:08:26,010 --> 00:08:28,340
I know you came for the treasure map.

149
00:08:29,150 --> 00:08:30,720
I won't let you succeed.

150
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:33,840
Principal Cheng, there's no rush about the treasure map.

151
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,600
Today,

152
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:36,760
I have come specifically to visit you.

153
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:38,220
Cut the crap.

154
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,860
We need to find Mr. Guo.

155
00:08:49,860 --> 00:08:51,910
He must know the whereabouts of Shaoyi.

156
00:08:51,910 --> 00:08:53,070
How can he be a teacher,

157
00:08:53,070 --> 00:08:54,190
watching his own student

158
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:54,730
[Casino]

159
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,500
being in danger and doing nothing?

160
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:56,580
[Casino]

161
00:08:55,630 --> 00:08:57,560
I'll beat him up next time I see him.

162
00:09:28,220 --> 00:09:29,800
The Iron Fan Scholar Cheng Mufei.

163
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:32,500
You truly live up to your name.

164
00:09:32,610 --> 00:09:33,630
But you probably wouldn't

165
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:35,150
want people around here

166
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:38,520
to know why you're out here so late at night.

167
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:40,080
I went to the government

168
00:09:40,310 --> 00:09:42,630
and found something interesting.

169
00:09:42,650 --> 00:09:45,070
The reason the body was dismembered

170
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,790
wasn't because the killer was cruel,

171
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:48,550
but because the killer

172
00:09:48,990 --> 00:09:50,720
wanted to hide one thing.

173
00:09:50,990 --> 00:09:51,800
That man

174
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:53,630
was killed by the Blood Technique.

175
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:54,560
So what?

176
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:55,440
Cheng Mufei.

177
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:56,640
You

178
00:09:57,430 --> 00:09:58,910
have studied the Blood Technique, haven't you?

179
00:09:58,910 --> 00:09:59,950
Ridiculous.

180
00:10:15,820 --> 00:10:17,620
Why not use the Blood Technique?

181
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,670
If you use the Blood Technique,

182
00:10:19,670 --> 00:10:22,150
you can control your reversed meridians.

183
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:24,680
Use it. Use the Blood Technique!

184
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:35,940
You guessed wrong.

185
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:38,760
I don't

186
00:10:39,190 --> 00:10:41,270
and can't use the Blood Technique.

187
00:10:41,340 --> 00:10:42,490
Prepare to die.

188
00:10:52,430 --> 00:10:53,150
Mr. Guo.

189
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,590
Mr. Guo.

190
00:11:09,160 --> 00:11:10,510
Qiao, don't be afraid.

191
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,560
I was overwhelmed

192
00:11:23,710 --> 00:11:24,820
with debts

193
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,450
and couldn't face my family and students.

194
00:11:29,190 --> 00:11:30,520
Inform the government.

195
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:32,920
What's all this mess?

196
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:34,680
Just as we had a lead on the dismemberment case,

197
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:37,010
now there's a gambler who hanged himself.

198
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:38,590
Wait.

199
00:11:40,430 --> 00:11:41,490
Young Master Duan.

200
00:11:41,990 --> 00:11:44,360
Is there any progress on the dismemberment case?

201
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,710
The victim is a woman.

202
00:11:45,790 --> 00:11:47,170
But unfortunately, her appearance was ruined.

203
00:11:47,170 --> 00:11:48,550
We will continue the investigation.

204
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,200
Okay.

205
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:50,430
Thank you.

206
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:51,790
Goodbye.

207
00:11:53,950 --> 00:11:54,950
Principal Cheng.

208
00:12:01,590 --> 00:12:02,320
Uncle Cheng.

209
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:03,190
Duan Yu.

210
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:06,670
Why did you find Mr. Guo's body?

211
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:07,800
We found...

212
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,910
We found out that Mr. Guo and Shaoyi had conflicts

213
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:12,270
and suspected that Mr. Guo was hiding Shaoyi's whereabouts.

214
00:12:12,270 --> 00:12:13,330
We came to inquire.

215
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:15,310
But when we arrived...

216
00:12:15,950 --> 00:12:17,630
I heard he was overwhelmed with debts

217
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:18,830
and saw no way out.

218
00:12:18,950 --> 00:12:20,830
Have you found any clues about Shaoyi?

219
00:12:20,830 --> 00:12:21,710
No.

220
00:12:22,230 --> 00:12:23,320
When we arrived,

221
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,520
he was already gone.

222
00:12:25,350 --> 00:12:26,870
God will bless him.

223
00:12:26,990 --> 00:12:28,160
Shaoyi is a good child.

224
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:29,510
He will surely be safe.

225
00:12:29,630 --> 00:12:31,120
Since a murder just occurred here,

226
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:32,520
you shouldn't stay long.

227
00:12:32,590 --> 00:12:35,270
I will handle things with the government.

228
00:12:35,350 --> 00:12:36,230
Go back now.

229
00:12:36,350 --> 00:12:37,110
Uncle Cheng.

230
00:12:37,660 --> 00:12:39,120
You're not in good health.

231
00:12:39,190 --> 00:12:41,590
Let's call some teachers from the academy to handle this.

232
00:12:41,590 --> 00:12:42,920
It's a tumultuous time,

233
00:12:43,470 --> 00:12:45,230
let's not burden others.

234
00:12:45,250 --> 00:12:46,590
Go back. Don't worry.

235
00:12:47,110 --> 00:12:48,510
I'll go in and take a look.

236
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:53,640
The Principal is really a good person.

237
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:56,670
But Shaoyi's trail has gone cold again.

238
00:12:57,430 --> 00:12:58,830
There's always a way out.

239
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:00,200
We will find a solution.

240
00:13:01,730 --> 00:13:02,580
Have you heard?

241
00:13:02,330 --> 00:13:06,580
[Jizhou Academy]

242
00:13:02,670 --> 00:13:04,000
Mr. Guo has passed away.

243
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:05,030
Really?

244
00:13:05,190 --> 00:13:06,790
I just attended his class two days ago.

245
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:07,880
This is too sudden.

246
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,910
Do you think there's something wrong

247
00:13:09,910 --> 00:13:11,670
with our academy's feng shui?

248
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,750
The Principal's wife has been ill for a long time.

249
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:15,360
The Principal is weakening day by day.

250
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,710
Duan Shaoyi has mysteriously disappeared.

251
00:13:16,710 --> 00:13:19,110
And now Mr. Guo has died.

252
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,430
The subjects on which the Master did not talk,
were extraordinary things, feats of strength, disorder, and spiritual beings.

253
00:13:20,430 --> 00:13:21,350
Stop it.

254
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:22,310
Principal Cheng is here.

255
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:24,480
[Jizhou Academy]

256
00:13:23,310 --> 00:13:24,430
Hurry up.

257
00:13:31,470 --> 00:13:32,720
Everyone should be aware of

258
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:34,120
Mr. Guo's passing by now.

259
00:13:34,190 --> 00:13:40,040
[Jizhou Academy]

260
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:35,870
From now on,

261
00:13:36,430 --> 00:13:38,240
be extra careful when you go out.

262
00:13:39,950 --> 00:13:41,880
Principal Cheng, what about Shaoyi?

263
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,140
Has Shaoyi been found?

264
00:13:43,150 --> 00:13:45,190
His uncle questioned me a few days ago.

265
00:13:45,190 --> 00:13:46,250
What did he ask you?

266
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:48,360
About the last time I saw Shaoyi.

267
00:13:48,710 --> 00:13:50,270
I said he had an appointment.

268
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:51,390
He left in a hurry.

269
00:13:51,470 --> 00:13:53,470
Do you know who he met and where he went?

270
00:13:53,470 --> 00:13:54,670
I don't know.

271
00:13:58,070 --> 00:13:59,510
Why didn't you tell Principal Cheng

272
00:13:59,510 --> 00:14:00,970
about the luminous pearl?

273
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,900
I thought you trusted him.

274
00:14:05,210 --> 00:14:06,670
Mr. Guo's death was suspicious.

275
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:08,870
We all know he used the luminous pearl to pay off his debts.

276
00:14:08,870 --> 00:14:10,550
It's impossible for him to commit suicide over debts.

277
00:14:10,550 --> 00:14:13,560
This means the murderer doesn't know where the luminous pearl is.

278
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:15,320
It's not that I don't trust Uncle Cheng.

279
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:17,720
But the luminous pearl is our only clue.

280
00:14:17,990 --> 00:14:19,190
It's very important.

281
00:14:20,470 --> 00:14:22,130
Then what should we do with it?

282
00:14:22,590 --> 00:14:23,470
Hide it?

283
00:14:23,670 --> 00:14:24,320
No.

284
00:14:24,590 --> 00:14:26,320
I will return it to the casino.

285
00:14:26,710 --> 00:14:29,040
If the murderer wants to hide his murders,

286
00:14:29,670 --> 00:14:31,720
he will definitely find the luminous pearl

287
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:33,950
and don't let others have anything on him.

288
00:14:33,950 --> 00:14:35,790
You want the owner of the casino

289
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:38,000
to spread the news about the luminous pearl

290
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:40,520
to lure out the person most concerned about its whereabouts.

291
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:41,160
Exactly.

292
00:14:42,110 --> 00:14:43,190
From today onwards,

293
00:14:43,190 --> 00:14:45,510
we must pretend to give up looking for Shaoyi.

294
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:48,640
Only then will the killer lower his guard

295
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:49,910
and reveal himself.

296
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:51,280
Got it. I'll go now.

297
00:14:52,950 --> 00:14:54,230
It's been six days.

298
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,840
Why hasn't Shaoyi returned?

299
00:14:57,910 --> 00:14:59,270
Let me out!

300
00:15:00,390 --> 00:15:01,790
Let me out!

301
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:06,040
Why am I so unlucky?

302
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:34,350
I didn't expect Madam to be a member of the Sacred Blood Sect.

303
00:15:34,770 --> 00:15:36,730
No, I can't give up.

304
00:15:37,630 --> 00:15:39,670
I have to escape and tell Uncle.

305
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:56,640
I don't believe

306
00:15:56,670 --> 00:15:58,030
I can't open this.

307
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:21,750
No way.

308
00:16:30,260 --> 00:16:32,400
Silver needles, wrist arrows

309
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:33,750
and darts.

310
00:16:36,300 --> 00:16:37,500
What else do you have?

311
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:40,510
Take them all out.

312
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:43,030
There's nothing more.

313
00:16:43,030 --> 00:16:44,110
Really.

314
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:45,990
Take off the ring.

315
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:48,680
This ring is my grandfather's keepsake.

316
00:16:48,680 --> 00:16:50,710
It represents my remembrance of him.

317
00:16:50,710 --> 00:16:52,550
Your grandpa and I are old friends.

318
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:54,190
He never wore things like this.

319
00:16:54,190 --> 00:16:54,960
Shaoyi,

320
00:16:55,070 --> 00:16:57,270
your small tricks with the contraption

321
00:16:57,270 --> 00:16:59,120
cannot fool me.

322
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,320
Grandpa Cheng,

323
00:17:01,760 --> 00:17:03,390
do you really have to do this?

324
00:17:06,190 --> 00:17:08,910
Our Duan family have been friends with you for generations.

325
00:17:08,910 --> 00:17:10,510
Can't you let me out?

326
00:17:10,630 --> 00:17:11,470
Shaoyi.

327
00:17:12,359 --> 00:17:14,589
Why did you sneak in to find your Madam?

328
00:17:14,950 --> 00:17:16,640
She has always been nice to me.

329
00:17:16,990 --> 00:17:18,599
I knew she doesn't have tuberculosis.

330
00:17:18,599 --> 00:17:20,390
I was worried she might be in some trouble.

331
00:17:20,390 --> 00:17:22,520
But you wouldn't let anyone visit her,

332
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,270
so I sneaked in to check on her.

333
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:25,829
I'm glad

334
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,270
you care about her.

335
00:17:27,710 --> 00:17:29,950
You've seen something you shouldn't have.

336
00:17:29,950 --> 00:17:30,670
No.

337
00:17:30,790 --> 00:17:32,190
I haven't seen anything.

338
00:17:32,630 --> 00:17:34,000
Please don't kill me.

339
00:17:34,120 --> 00:17:35,670
I won't kill you.

340
00:17:38,230 --> 00:17:39,670
Grandpa Cheng, I...

341
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:44,260
Who are you?

342
00:17:44,430 --> 00:17:46,590
You're indeed the Young Master of the Duan family.

343
00:17:46,590 --> 00:17:47,560
Cheng Mufei.

344
00:17:47,790 --> 00:17:49,230
We can cooperate.

345
00:17:49,520 --> 00:17:51,550
I will help you save your wife.

346
00:17:52,790 --> 00:17:53,830
Prepare to die!

347
00:17:54,390 --> 00:17:56,280
She doesn't have long to live, does she?

348
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:57,240
What did you say?

349
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:02,190
I went to the government.

350
00:18:02,190 --> 00:18:04,630
And naturally I learned that you dismembered that woman

351
00:18:04,630 --> 00:18:06,430
to cover up the Blood Technique.

352
00:18:06,510 --> 00:18:08,750
While you can fool others,

353
00:18:08,910 --> 00:18:10,590
I could tell at a glance

354
00:18:11,080 --> 00:18:14,550
that the one who used the Blood Technique was about to die.

355
00:18:14,570 --> 00:18:15,600
Stop talking nonsense.

356
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:18,330
You know very well whether I'm talking nonsense.

357
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:19,590
What I want to say

358
00:18:19,950 --> 00:18:21,000
is that I can save her.

359
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:21,990
Is that true?

360
00:18:22,110 --> 00:18:23,270
Of course.

361
00:18:23,710 --> 00:18:25,230
Except for the Master of the Sacred Blood Sect,

362
00:18:25,230 --> 00:18:27,090
who else is confident to save her?

363
00:18:28,180 --> 00:18:29,110
What do you want?

364
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:31,830
The treasure map.

365
00:18:32,610 --> 00:18:34,440
With Duan Shaoyi as bait,

366
00:18:34,590 --> 00:18:37,330
Duan Yan will surely give you the treasure map.

367
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:40,100
I agreed to help you get the treasure map,

368
00:18:40,590 --> 00:18:42,780
but I never said I'd use Shaoyi as bait.

369
00:18:43,510 --> 00:18:44,560
Bait?

370
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:46,870
Are you from the Sacred Blood Sect?

371
00:18:46,870 --> 00:18:49,260
Duan Shaoyi, don't you understand?

372
00:18:49,430 --> 00:18:51,800
I am the greatest enemy of the Duan family,

373
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:53,910
the Master of the Sacred Blood Sect.

374
00:18:53,910 --> 00:18:54,830
Grandpa Cheng.

375
00:18:55,110 --> 00:18:56,520
How could you cooperate with him?

376
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:58,990
You and my grandfather are sworn brothers.

377
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:01,360
I've treated you as my own grandfather since young.

378
00:19:01,360 --> 00:19:03,290
You cannot betray the Duan family.

379
00:19:03,630 --> 00:19:04,440
Shaoyi.

380
00:19:04,630 --> 00:19:05,560
I'm sorry.

381
00:19:06,590 --> 00:19:07,910
What I can do now

382
00:19:07,910 --> 00:19:09,430
is to save your life.

383
00:19:09,550 --> 00:19:11,310
You care so much for your Madam, right?

384
00:19:11,310 --> 00:19:13,510
She indeed doesn't have tuberculosis,

385
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:15,310
but she doesn't have long to live.

386
00:19:15,310 --> 00:19:17,560
For your Madam's sake, I can only make you suffer.

387
00:19:17,560 --> 00:19:19,110
As long as I get the treasure map,

388
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:20,990
I will let you go safely.

389
00:19:21,100 --> 00:19:23,190
I will confess all the sins

390
00:19:23,270 --> 00:19:24,270
and bear all the guilt then.

391
00:19:24,270 --> 00:19:25,130
Grandpa Cheng,

392
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:27,510
you are the Principal of Jizhou Academy,

393
00:19:27,510 --> 00:19:29,230
the head of the righteous sect,

394
00:19:29,230 --> 00:19:30,590
and my Master.

395
00:19:30,870 --> 00:19:33,350
Shaoyi, I'm sorry.

396
00:19:34,270 --> 00:19:36,030
But there's no turning back.

397
00:19:40,030 --> 00:19:41,550
She's indeed a member of my sect.

398
00:19:41,550 --> 00:19:42,400
Cheng Mufei.

399
00:19:42,550 --> 00:19:44,040
I didn't expect your wife

400
00:19:44,700 --> 00:19:46,830
to be a member of the Sacred Blood Sect.

401
00:19:46,990 --> 00:19:48,590
Xueniang is different.

402
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:50,320
She lost her memory long ago

403
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:52,110
and knew nothing about her identity.

404
00:19:52,110 --> 00:19:53,960
No wonder she became so weak.

405
00:19:53,990 --> 00:19:55,720
She was born with deficiencies

406
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:58,870
and needs the Blood Technique to supplement her vitality.

407
00:19:58,870 --> 00:20:01,830
Last time Shaoyi interrupted her Blood Technique,

408
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:03,550
it backfired.

409
00:20:03,790 --> 00:20:06,160
And she refused to use it again,

410
00:20:06,280 --> 00:20:08,830
leading to her current condition.

411
00:20:09,630 --> 00:20:12,670
I knew this long ago.

412
00:20:13,890 --> 00:20:15,910
No wonder she hid here for over ten years

413
00:20:15,910 --> 00:20:16,890
without being found.

414
00:20:16,890 --> 00:20:20,240
It's because you've been nourishing her with your own blood.

415
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,430
Cheng Mufei,

416
00:20:21,560 --> 00:20:25,030
I didn't expect you to be so devoted to her.

417
00:20:25,150 --> 00:20:28,030
It's none of your business.

418
00:20:28,110 --> 00:20:30,110
Cheng Mufei, join our sect.

419
00:20:30,380 --> 00:20:32,510
Only as a member of the Sacred Blood Sect,

420
00:20:32,510 --> 00:20:34,790
can you be on the same team and share life and death

421
00:20:34,790 --> 00:20:36,230
with your wife.

422
00:20:36,350 --> 00:20:37,520
Stop talking.

423
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:42,920
Here's the treasure map you wanted.

424
00:20:44,390 --> 00:20:46,190
Hurry and save Xueniang.

425
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:51,990
I have a Biluo pill

426
00:20:51,990 --> 00:20:55,830
that can alleviate the pain from the backlash of the Blood Technique.

427
00:20:55,830 --> 00:20:57,590
As long as you let her eat this,

428
00:21:01,140 --> 00:21:02,600
she will wake up

429
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:04,750
within three days.

430
00:21:12,150 --> 00:21:14,950
But a single pill is not enough to save her.

431
00:21:15,070 --> 00:21:16,160
What do you want me to do?

432
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:18,800
I want the treasure map in Duan Yan's hands.

433
00:21:18,830 --> 00:21:20,760
Duan Yan's son is now in your hands.

434
00:21:21,370 --> 00:21:22,640
Whether you kill him

435
00:21:22,710 --> 00:21:23,910
or take advantage of him,

436
00:21:23,910 --> 00:21:25,920
as long as you get the treasure map,

437
00:21:26,110 --> 00:21:28,420
I'll give you another Biluo pill.

438
00:21:28,460 --> 00:21:30,150
What if you break your promise?

439
00:21:30,150 --> 00:21:32,270
Cheng Mufei, do you have any other choice?

440
00:21:32,270 --> 00:21:34,470
Only I can save Xueniang.

441
00:21:37,010 --> 00:21:38,600
Two Biluo pills

442
00:21:38,990 --> 00:21:42,760
will ensure she is no longer controlled by the Blood Technique.

443
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:45,080
Isn't that what you want?

444
00:21:45,470 --> 00:21:47,670
Young Master, everything is arranged.

445
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:50,190
The casino owner will release the news today

446
00:21:50,190 --> 00:21:52,070
that he has a luminous pearl.

447
00:21:52,310 --> 00:21:53,950
If anyone comes to ask about it,

448
00:21:53,950 --> 00:21:55,880
he will record his identity.

449
00:21:56,350 --> 00:21:57,190
I found

450
00:21:57,310 --> 00:21:59,790
some signs of a struggle in Mr. Guo's house.

451
00:22:00,550 --> 00:22:02,920
Someone must have been there before he died.

452
00:22:02,920 --> 00:22:04,580
Should we urge the government

453
00:22:04,760 --> 00:22:06,350
to investigate the cause of Mr. Guo's death again?

454
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:08,110
I went to mourn him and persuaded his family

455
00:22:08,110 --> 00:22:09,950
to ask the government to reopen the case.

456
00:22:09,950 --> 00:22:12,360
Perhaps this will force the murderer out.

457
00:22:14,460 --> 00:22:15,340
Have you heard?

458
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:18,800
[Jizhou Academy]

459
00:22:15,470 --> 00:22:17,120
The government has reopened the case.

460
00:22:17,120 --> 00:22:17,960
Reopened the case?

461
00:22:17,960 --> 00:22:19,310
Mr. Guo did not commit suicide.

462
00:22:19,310 --> 00:22:20,280
It was a murder.

463
00:22:20,310 --> 00:22:20,990
Murder?

464
00:22:21,010 --> 00:22:21,660
Yes.

465
00:22:21,950 --> 00:22:22,800
How is that possible?

466
00:22:22,800 --> 00:22:24,120
I don't know.

467
00:22:37,710 --> 00:22:38,390
Could it be

468
00:22:38,710 --> 00:22:40,570
that it was hidden in the academy?

469
00:22:56,950 --> 00:22:57,800
Uncle Cheng.

470
00:23:00,150 --> 00:23:01,150
Why are you here?

471
00:23:01,710 --> 00:23:04,350
The government said that Mr. Guo did not commit suicide,

472
00:23:04,350 --> 00:23:06,480
so I came to see if there were any clues.

473
00:23:06,550 --> 00:23:08,590
What if Mr. Guo's death is related to Shaoyi?

474
00:23:08,590 --> 00:23:10,190
You thought the same as I did.

475
00:23:10,390 --> 00:23:11,650
Did you find anything?

476
00:23:11,790 --> 00:23:13,110
Most of Mr. Guo's belongings

477
00:23:13,110 --> 00:23:14,670
were taken by his family.

478
00:23:14,840 --> 00:23:16,110
I found nothing.

479
00:23:17,630 --> 00:23:18,830
If you find anything,

480
00:23:18,870 --> 00:23:20,240
please inform me immediately.

481
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:21,000
Sure.

482
00:23:21,710 --> 00:23:24,200
The Master of the Duan family of Changqing is here to visit.

483
00:23:24,200 --> 00:23:25,150
Is Principal Cheng here?

484
00:23:24,940 --> 00:23:31,470
[Jizhou Academy]

485
00:23:25,230 --> 00:23:26,320
Please come in.

486
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:27,580
His Lordship, please.

487
00:23:28,840 --> 00:23:29,840
This way, please.

488
00:23:30,670 --> 00:23:33,680
I was attacked on my way back a few days ago.

489
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:36,350
It seems that the Sacred Blood Sect has mobilized all their forces.

490
00:23:36,350 --> 00:23:37,960
Thinking about your safety and that of the academy,

491
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:39,220
I'm really worried.

492
00:23:39,280 --> 00:23:42,270
I haven't seen any traces of the Sacred Blood Sect in Jizhou yet.

493
00:23:42,270 --> 00:23:43,680
Maybe their next target

494
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:45,030
is Xiling.

495
00:23:45,070 --> 00:23:46,030
That's right.

496
00:23:46,140 --> 00:23:48,400
I've already sent people to support Xiling,

497
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:50,400
but I haven't received any news yet.

498
00:23:51,110 --> 00:23:51,750
By the way,

499
00:23:52,490 --> 00:23:54,190
I haven't seen your wife.

500
00:23:54,590 --> 00:23:55,750
How is she?

501
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:58,140
Xueniang still has the same old illness.

502
00:23:58,230 --> 00:23:59,750
She just needs to rest.

503
00:24:00,110 --> 00:24:01,400
Thanks for your concern.

504
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:03,920
I brought a lot of nutritious medicine here.

505
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:05,460
It might be useful to her.

506
00:24:05,460 --> 00:24:06,560
There's one thing

507
00:24:07,110 --> 00:24:10,040
you might not know yet since you came all the way here.

508
00:24:10,110 --> 00:24:10,790
What is it?

509
00:24:10,870 --> 00:24:12,030
I'm sorry.

510
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:13,310
Shaoyi...

511
00:24:14,310 --> 00:24:15,190
He has gone missing.

512
00:24:15,190 --> 00:24:16,040
What?

513
00:24:16,310 --> 00:24:18,880
Duan Yu came all the way from Changqing to look for him,

514
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:19,950
but there has been

515
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,430
no progress these days.

516
00:24:21,430 --> 00:24:22,490
Duan Yu is here too.

517
00:24:22,910 --> 00:24:23,640
Where is he?

518
00:24:23,750 --> 00:24:25,790
I've arranged for him to stay at the academy,

519
00:24:25,790 --> 00:24:26,390
but

520
00:24:26,830 --> 00:24:28,300
he brought a woman with him

521
00:24:28,470 --> 00:24:30,790
who seems very close to him.

522
00:24:30,910 --> 00:24:31,830
A woman?

523
00:24:32,230 --> 00:24:33,670
It seems to be called

524
00:24:34,520 --> 00:24:35,750
Qiao.

525
00:24:44,270 --> 00:24:46,190
Miss Gu has not rested well

526
00:24:46,630 --> 00:24:48,480
since she returned from Xiling.

527
00:24:48,870 --> 00:24:50,630
It seems she is really tired.

528
00:24:53,510 --> 00:24:55,670
Indeed, she has been very busy lately.

529
00:24:56,230 --> 00:24:57,960
But she never says she's tired.

530
00:24:59,360 --> 00:25:00,550
I neglected her.

531
00:25:01,870 --> 00:25:02,670
Young Master.

532
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:04,830
It seems you and Miss Gu

533
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:07,150
have been getting along very well recently.

534
00:25:07,150 --> 00:25:10,230
Are you and Miss Gu about to get married?

535
00:25:11,750 --> 00:25:13,860
Keep your voice down. Don't wake her up.

536
00:25:13,860 --> 00:25:14,360
Shush.

537
00:25:18,840 --> 00:25:20,950
His Lordship, listen to me.

538
00:25:21,610 --> 00:25:22,600
Mr. Qi.

539
00:25:22,800 --> 00:25:24,800
Take down this incompetent person.

540
00:25:24,950 --> 00:25:25,630
Yes.

541
00:25:26,270 --> 00:25:27,200
-Kneel!
-Kneel!

542
00:25:27,560 --> 00:25:28,230
Brother.

543
00:25:30,970 --> 00:25:31,680
Duan Yu.

544
00:25:32,050 --> 00:25:33,850
Hand over the Star of Rebellion!

545
00:25:40,630 --> 00:25:42,290
How can you be so foolish?

546
00:25:42,770 --> 00:25:45,400
Shaoyi's disappearance is certainly related to the Star of Rebellion.

547
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:47,060
You must have been used by her.

548
00:25:47,190 --> 00:25:49,060
Qiao and I have been together all the time.

549
00:25:49,060 --> 00:25:50,020
I can confirm

550
00:25:50,270 --> 00:25:51,910
she has nothing to do with this.

551
00:25:51,910 --> 00:25:53,830
How can you be so reckless?

552
00:25:54,310 --> 00:25:56,040
Do you know that the Xu family, one of the four great families,

553
00:25:56,040 --> 00:25:57,120
has betrayed us

554
00:25:57,140 --> 00:25:58,510
and joined the Sacred Blood Sect?

555
00:25:58,510 --> 00:25:59,880
Do you know I was attacked

556
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,510
by the Sacred Blood Sect on my way here?

557
00:26:01,510 --> 00:26:03,840
The Sacred Blood Sect crisis is imminent,

558
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:05,780
yet you remain obstinate,

559
00:26:05,950 --> 00:26:07,820
siding with the Star of Rebellion.

560
00:26:07,820 --> 00:26:09,570
She has no collusion with the Sacred Blood Sect.

561
00:26:09,570 --> 00:26:11,570
You must have been bewitched by her.

562
00:26:12,150 --> 00:26:14,000
The Star of Rebellion is the enemy of the Duan family

563
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:16,510
and the key to the Sacred Blood Sect's return.

564
00:26:16,510 --> 00:26:17,870
Since you can't do it,

565
00:26:19,110 --> 00:26:20,800
I'll kill her myself.

566
00:26:20,950 --> 00:26:23,000
Brother, please think twice.

567
00:26:23,510 --> 00:26:24,350
Brother.

568
00:26:25,320 --> 00:26:26,750
Our enemy is the Sacred Blood Sect.

569
00:26:26,750 --> 00:26:27,750
Although Qiao...

570
00:26:28,300 --> 00:26:29,990
Although Gu Qingqiao is the Star of Rebellion,

571
00:26:29,990 --> 00:26:31,710
she has never done anything heinous.

572
00:26:31,710 --> 00:26:33,240
Then why does she want to gather the Four Treasures?

573
00:26:33,240 --> 00:26:36,590
She wants to gather the Four Treasures to return to her world.

574
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:38,770
She has told me all about her background and purpose.

575
00:26:38,770 --> 00:26:40,600
She will never side with the Sacred Blood Sect

576
00:26:40,600 --> 00:26:42,030
or become an enemy of the Duan family.

577
00:26:42,030 --> 00:26:43,830
That's just her side of the story.

578
00:26:43,830 --> 00:26:44,590
Step aside!

579
00:26:44,830 --> 00:26:46,760
Don't blame me for being ruthless!

580
00:26:53,020 --> 00:26:53,820
Young Master.

581
00:26:55,140 --> 00:26:55,900
Duan Yu.

582
00:26:57,550 --> 00:26:58,700
Star of Rebellion.

583
00:27:01,510 --> 00:27:03,770
Lord Duan, it has nothing to do with Duan Yu.

584
00:27:03,770 --> 00:27:05,510
Come at me if you have anything to settle.

585
00:27:05,510 --> 00:27:06,390
Qiao.

586
00:27:06,990 --> 00:27:08,050
Don't be reckless.

587
00:27:08,270 --> 00:27:09,150
Master Duan,

588
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:11,200
I swear that I have never intended to

589
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,880
be an enemy of the Duan family.

590
00:27:12,910 --> 00:27:14,710
Do you think I would believe you?

591
00:27:14,780 --> 00:27:15,860
Shaoyi has encountered mishaps

592
00:27:15,860 --> 00:27:17,450
several times after being with you.

593
00:27:17,450 --> 00:27:18,700
Who would believe

594
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:20,270
it has nothing to do with you?

595
00:27:20,270 --> 00:27:21,110
Qiao!

596
00:27:32,970 --> 00:27:34,010
Master.

597
00:27:41,050 --> 00:27:41,720
This is...

598
00:27:42,110 --> 00:27:43,780
This is one of the Four Treasures.

599
00:27:43,780 --> 00:27:44,920
Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

600
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:47,270
Xiling gave the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword to her.

601
00:27:47,270 --> 00:27:48,220
Not only that.

602
00:27:48,730 --> 00:27:50,860
Qiao is also a disciple of Xiling Sect.

603
00:27:51,180 --> 00:27:52,560
She's a disciple of Wang Tianshan.

604
00:27:52,560 --> 00:27:53,810
This Black Wood Human-shaped Sword

605
00:27:53,810 --> 00:27:55,200
was obtained for her

606
00:27:55,520 --> 00:27:56,770
at the cost of Ruan Siqiong's life.

607
00:27:56,770 --> 00:27:58,060
Ruan Siqiong is dead?

608
00:27:58,290 --> 00:28:00,360
Didn't Xiling Sect know she is the Star of Rebellion?

609
00:28:00,360 --> 00:28:01,310
Master Ruan knew.

610
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:05,240
But he also knew that I wouldn't use the Four Treasures to do bad things.

611
00:28:21,030 --> 00:28:22,170
The treasure map.

612
00:28:22,630 --> 00:28:23,630
The treasure map?

613
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:26,370
Fifteen years ago,

614
00:28:26,370 --> 00:28:28,110
in order to quell the disputes in the Martial Arts World,

615
00:28:28,110 --> 00:28:30,630
my father eliminated the possibility of the Sacred Blood Sect's resurgence,

616
00:28:30,630 --> 00:28:32,040
and hid the Heavenly Pearl of the Four Treasures

617
00:28:32,040 --> 00:28:33,830
in an unknown location.

618
00:28:33,850 --> 00:28:35,000
He then drew a treasure map

619
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:36,690
of the hiding place,

620
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:38,370
divided it into four parts,

621
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:40,180
and entrusted each part to one of the four great families.

622
00:28:40,180 --> 00:28:41,330
The piece she holds

623
00:28:41,630 --> 00:28:43,510
is the one held by Xiling Sect.

624
00:28:43,670 --> 00:28:44,780
But I didn't expect

625
00:28:45,110 --> 00:28:47,110
Great Master Zhang to give it to her.

626
00:28:50,670 --> 00:28:51,640
Wait.

627
00:29:10,800 --> 00:29:13,460
If Great Master Zhang trusts Gu Qingqiao so much

628
00:29:13,490 --> 00:29:15,090
to give her the treasure map,

629
00:29:15,380 --> 00:29:17,580
it means Gu Qingqiao is very reliable.

630
00:29:17,710 --> 00:29:20,140
Great Master Zhang is over a hundred years old.

631
00:29:20,140 --> 00:29:21,490
Maybe he is senile.

632
00:29:21,670 --> 00:29:23,400
Don't insult the Great Master.

633
00:29:26,470 --> 00:29:28,630
You are quite protective of Great Master Zhang.

634
00:29:28,630 --> 00:29:30,360
Xiling disciples are united.

635
00:29:30,710 --> 00:29:32,780
Insulting the sect is the same as insulting me.

636
00:29:32,780 --> 00:29:34,030
Don't think I will let it slide

637
00:29:34,030 --> 00:29:35,590
just because you're Duan Yu's brother.

638
00:29:35,590 --> 00:29:37,190
If you had endured silently,

639
00:29:37,230 --> 00:29:39,090
I might not have spared your life.

640
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:41,080
But seeing how you protect them,

641
00:29:41,110 --> 00:29:42,920
you have earned my respect.

642
00:29:44,270 --> 00:29:45,070
Brother,

643
00:29:45,350 --> 00:29:47,510
this is not the time for internal strife.

644
00:29:47,510 --> 00:29:48,570
Shaoyi is missing,

645
00:29:48,590 --> 00:29:50,990
and the Sacred Blood Sect is pressing hard.

646
00:29:51,270 --> 00:29:52,470
Being on the same side

647
00:29:52,750 --> 00:29:54,150
is actually a good thing.

648
00:29:57,430 --> 00:29:58,540
To me,

649
00:29:58,590 --> 00:30:00,790
the most important things are friends and family.

650
00:30:00,790 --> 00:30:02,070
Shaoyi's disappearance

651
00:30:02,070 --> 00:30:03,950
is surely related to the Sacred Blood Sect.

652
00:30:03,950 --> 00:30:05,140
I cannot sit idly by.

653
00:30:08,640 --> 00:30:09,710
The treasure map

654
00:30:10,230 --> 00:30:12,760
will be more useful in your hands than in mine.

655
00:30:13,710 --> 00:30:14,910
I'll give you the map.

656
00:30:28,630 --> 00:30:30,230
Let's find Shaoyi together.

657
00:30:30,990 --> 00:30:33,580
Aren't you afraid I will destroy the treasure map,

658
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:36,040
so you will never obtain the Four Treasures?

659
00:30:38,870 --> 00:30:39,910
If that happens,

660
00:30:40,560 --> 00:30:41,510
it's my fate.

661
00:30:41,910 --> 00:30:42,790
For Shaoyi,

662
00:30:43,350 --> 00:30:44,280
I accept my fate.

663
00:30:44,750 --> 00:30:46,870
For the sake of Great Master Zhang,

664
00:30:48,110 --> 00:30:49,370
I will spare your life.

665
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:50,630
Thank you, Brother.

666
00:30:52,830 --> 00:30:53,830
Gu Qingqiao.

667
00:30:53,990 --> 00:30:56,400
I didn't expect you to trust Duan Yu so much.

668
00:30:56,430 --> 00:30:57,550
You handed the treasure map

669
00:30:57,550 --> 00:30:59,410
to someone who wanted to kill you.

670
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:00,590
Calm down, My Lord.

671
00:31:00,590 --> 00:31:02,440
The old fox Zhang Sifeng

672
00:31:02,560 --> 00:31:05,660
hid the treasure map in the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword

673
00:31:05,660 --> 00:31:07,260
but didn't tell Gu Qingqiao.

674
00:31:07,450 --> 00:31:08,600
In this way,

675
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:10,630
he protected both Gu Qingqiao

676
00:31:10,790 --> 00:31:12,380
and the treasure map.

677
00:31:13,270 --> 00:31:15,080
What a cunning plan.

678
00:31:15,520 --> 00:31:17,840
With the three pieces of the treasure map are at Jizhou Academy,

679
00:31:17,840 --> 00:31:18,910
should we...

680
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:20,110
No hurry.

681
00:31:20,340 --> 00:31:22,430
There are many masters at Jizhou Academy.

682
00:31:22,430 --> 00:31:24,830
Don't take it by force if we can use wisdom.

683
00:31:25,060 --> 00:31:25,790
Yes.

684
00:31:27,310 --> 00:31:28,550
Cheng Mufei,

685
00:31:29,670 --> 00:31:31,770
don't let me down.

686
00:31:38,100 --> 00:31:39,100
It's disgusting.

687
00:31:39,210 --> 00:31:40,790
How can anyone do such work?

688
00:31:42,510 --> 00:31:44,750
Boss, look at this. What is this?

689
00:31:48,090 --> 00:31:49,900
This looks familiar.

690
00:31:50,030 --> 00:31:51,750
We believe the luminous pearl Mr. Guo used to pay off his debts

691
00:31:51,750 --> 00:31:52,840
is actually Shaoyi's.

692
00:31:52,840 --> 00:31:54,550
The murderer must have known about this oversight,

693
00:31:54,550 --> 00:31:56,510
so they killed him.

694
00:31:57,630 --> 00:31:58,590
Then

695
00:31:58,790 --> 00:32:00,520
where is the luminous pearl now?

696
00:32:00,520 --> 00:32:01,350
In the casino.

697
00:32:01,960 --> 00:32:03,670
If anyone inquires about the origin of the luminous pearl,

698
00:32:03,670 --> 00:32:05,930
he must have something to do with Shaoyi.

699
00:32:11,830 --> 00:32:13,430
His Lordship. Young Master.

700
00:32:15,520 --> 00:32:16,680
[Casino Entry Registration]

701
00:32:18,710 --> 00:32:20,390
This is the list sent by the casino,

702
00:32:20,390 --> 00:32:22,710
recording the people who inquired about
the luminous pearl in the past few days.

703
00:32:22,710 --> 00:32:23,830
Is there anyone suspicious?

704
00:32:23,830 --> 00:32:24,350
Yes.

705
00:32:24,470 --> 00:32:24,990
And

706
00:32:25,470 --> 00:32:26,790
it's someone unexpected.

707
00:32:26,790 --> 00:32:27,480
Who?

708
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:28,600
Principal Cheng.

709
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:31,590
Principal Cheng.

710
00:32:32,630 --> 00:32:33,580
Sheriff Song.

711
00:32:34,460 --> 00:32:35,670
We've asked around.

712
00:32:35,840 --> 00:32:38,900
Only the academy in all of Jizhou has such waist tokens,

713
00:32:39,390 --> 00:32:41,630
so we came to ask

714
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:44,830
if any women have gone missing from the academy.

715
00:32:44,830 --> 00:32:46,080
We have missing men,

716
00:32:46,230 --> 00:32:48,430
but no women that I know of.

717
00:32:48,790 --> 00:32:49,790
Even so,

718
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:51,750
please come by tomorrow

719
00:32:52,190 --> 00:32:53,270
to identify the body,

720
00:32:53,270 --> 00:32:55,320
just in case she is related to the academy.

721
00:32:55,320 --> 00:32:56,150
Impossible.

722
00:32:56,590 --> 00:32:57,910
Principal Cheng is highly respected.

723
00:32:57,910 --> 00:32:59,600
He has had good relations with the Duan family for many years,

724
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:01,190
and treats Shaoyi like his nephew.

725
00:33:01,190 --> 00:33:02,630
How could he harm Shaoyi?

726
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:04,250
There must be a mistake.

727
00:33:04,590 --> 00:33:06,050
I was also very surprised.

728
00:33:06,320 --> 00:33:07,070
But

729
00:33:07,270 --> 00:33:09,990
only Principal Cheng had contact with the Young Master Shaoyi.

730
00:33:09,990 --> 00:33:11,720
So I asked a few more questions.

731
00:33:11,840 --> 00:33:12,640
The owner said

732
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:16,180
Principal Cheng inquired about the price for his wife's birthday.

733
00:33:16,180 --> 00:33:17,150
This is normal.

734
00:33:17,630 --> 00:33:18,690
But other visitors

735
00:33:18,760 --> 00:33:20,990
only cared if the luminous pearl was real.

736
00:33:20,990 --> 00:33:22,030
Only Principal Cheng

737
00:33:22,030 --> 00:33:25,240
asked about where the luminous pearl came from.

738
00:33:25,750 --> 00:33:26,680
Maybe

739
00:33:27,030 --> 00:33:28,960
Principal Cheng was just curious.

740
00:33:29,270 --> 00:33:30,670
After all,

741
00:33:30,830 --> 00:33:34,090
most things in a casino are not coming from the right place.

742
00:33:35,270 --> 00:33:36,710
I remember you told me

743
00:33:36,820 --> 00:33:38,680
the last time you saw Mr. Guo,

744
00:33:39,020 --> 00:33:41,080
he was arguing with Principal Cheng.

745
00:33:41,110 --> 00:33:43,150
It might have been a regular argument.

746
00:33:43,150 --> 00:33:45,480
It can't be evidence of murdering Mr. Guo.

747
00:33:45,950 --> 00:33:48,150
I don't want to suspect Director Cheng.

748
00:33:48,630 --> 00:33:49,690
For Shaoyi's sake,

749
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:52,030
we must remain vigilant.

750
00:33:52,630 --> 00:33:53,910
Who could it be?

751
00:33:54,190 --> 00:33:56,790
The academy doesn't even admit female students.

752
00:33:56,790 --> 00:33:59,830
Could this waist token be left by the murderer?

753
00:33:59,950 --> 00:34:01,030
What's going on?

754
00:34:01,190 --> 00:34:02,050
Mr. Constable.

755
00:34:03,230 --> 00:34:04,760
Young Master Duan, Miss Gu.

756
00:34:05,030 --> 00:34:06,310
Any news on Shaoyi?

757
00:34:06,470 --> 00:34:08,400
Today we're not here for him.

758
00:34:08,989 --> 00:34:10,420
Then why are you here?

759
00:34:10,679 --> 00:34:12,630
Young Master Duan, has there been

760
00:34:12,710 --> 00:34:14,510
any woman missing from the academy recently?

761
00:34:14,510 --> 00:34:16,710
The academy only admits male students.

762
00:34:16,989 --> 00:34:19,120
Women are mostly students' servants,

763
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:21,550
or Principal Cheng's family.

764
00:34:23,239 --> 00:34:25,760
Why do you ask about the missing woman?

765
00:34:25,790 --> 00:34:27,590
Miss Gu, there's something you don't know.

766
00:34:27,590 --> 00:34:29,550
There's been progress in the dismembered body case.

767
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:30,949
We found this waist token

768
00:34:31,110 --> 00:34:32,510
on this body.

769
00:34:32,920 --> 00:34:34,920
Clearly, it belongs to the academy.

770
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:37,230
But we asked Principal Cheng

771
00:34:37,760 --> 00:34:40,889
and he said there were no missing women from the academy.

772
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,110
Okay.

773
00:34:42,550 --> 00:34:43,310
Thank you.

774
00:34:44,170 --> 00:34:45,370
We'll take our leave.

775
00:34:53,550 --> 00:34:54,630
Is it that

776
00:34:55,310 --> 00:34:57,710
you haven't seen the Principal's wife yet?

777
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:01,760
Duan Yu.

778
00:35:02,430 --> 00:35:03,750
Where are you going?

779
00:35:04,070 --> 00:35:04,800
Uncle Cheng.

780
00:35:04,990 --> 00:35:06,050
My brother asked me

781
00:35:06,110 --> 00:35:08,040
to give some supplements to Madam.

782
00:35:09,930 --> 00:35:10,890
Thank you.

783
00:35:11,570 --> 00:35:13,400
Uncle Cheng, we're all here.

784
00:35:13,430 --> 00:35:15,670
Please let us see her.

785
00:35:17,500 --> 00:35:19,630
Her illness is contagious.

786
00:35:19,700 --> 00:35:20,470
It's okay.

787
00:35:20,630 --> 00:35:22,140
Tuberculosis does not easily infect people.

788
00:35:22,140 --> 00:35:23,350
We'll be careful.

789
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:27,360
She's probably resting right now.

790
00:35:28,350 --> 00:35:30,150
We'll just take a look from afar.

791
00:35:32,110 --> 00:35:33,840
It wouldn't be appropriate...

792
00:35:34,300 --> 00:35:36,300
Uncle Cheng, please listen to me.

793
00:35:36,510 --> 00:35:37,650
What do you mean?

794
00:35:37,790 --> 00:35:40,230
Let me out!

795
00:35:45,080 --> 00:35:46,110
Is anyone there?

796
00:35:46,190 --> 00:35:47,640
Let me out!

797
00:36:09,070 --> 00:36:10,640
Xueniang. Xueniang.

798
00:36:12,470 --> 00:36:13,300
Xueniang.

799
00:36:13,420 --> 00:36:14,740
Are you all right?

800
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:16,930
I'm fine.

801
00:36:17,870 --> 00:36:18,910
Who's this?

802
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:21,910
Madam.

803
00:36:23,430 --> 00:36:24,630
Hello, Madam.

804
00:36:26,950 --> 00:36:28,100
You are...

805
00:36:31,670 --> 00:36:32,470
Yu.

806
00:36:32,690 --> 00:36:34,220
You remember me.

807
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:35,360
Of course.

808
00:36:35,610 --> 00:36:37,340
When you and Shaoyi were young,

809
00:36:37,920 --> 00:36:39,760
you often came to me for candy.

810
00:36:41,120 --> 00:36:41,960
Mufei.

811
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:43,720
Since Yu is here,

812
00:36:44,060 --> 00:36:45,320
why didn't you tell me?

813
00:36:45,340 --> 00:36:47,270
I'm worried about your condition.

814
00:36:47,310 --> 00:36:49,170
I'm also afraid they'll get sick.

815
00:36:52,080 --> 00:36:52,960
It doesn't matter.

816
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:55,400
I'm happy to see Yu.

817
00:36:58,720 --> 00:37:00,120
Who is this lady?

818
00:37:01,710 --> 00:37:03,470
I'm Duan Yu's friend.

819
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:05,200
I'm Gu Qingqiao.

820
00:37:06,290 --> 00:37:07,690
Shaoyi has gone missing.

821
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:09,840
Qiao is accompanying me to find him.

822
00:37:09,990 --> 00:37:12,390
Xueniang needs proper care for her illness.

823
00:37:12,390 --> 00:37:13,990
You've visited her.

824
00:37:14,080 --> 00:37:15,480
That's enough for today.

825
00:37:18,640 --> 00:37:19,320
Madam,

826
00:37:20,190 --> 00:37:22,120
these are the supplements for you.

827
00:37:23,150 --> 00:37:24,020
In that case,

828
00:37:24,310 --> 00:37:25,710
we'll take our leave now.

829
00:37:26,670 --> 00:37:27,550
Thank you.

830
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:41,900
Looks like we guessed wrong.

831
00:37:41,900 --> 00:37:44,240
That dismembered body isn't Madam.

832
00:37:44,830 --> 00:37:46,240
If it's not Madam,

833
00:37:46,630 --> 00:37:47,800
then who could it be?

834
00:37:50,110 --> 00:37:52,930
Xueniang, you've gotten scared today.

835
00:37:55,470 --> 00:37:56,260
Mufei.

836
00:37:57,030 --> 00:37:58,460
Why did you stop me?

837
00:37:59,030 --> 00:38:00,710
After killing Granny Xu

838
00:38:01,470 --> 00:38:05,130
and learning of my identity as a disciple of the Sacred Blood Sect,

839
00:38:05,190 --> 00:38:06,870
I should have died.

840
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:09,830
I can't keep dragging you down.

841
00:38:09,990 --> 00:38:12,910
There's no such thing between us.

842
00:38:13,500 --> 00:38:14,270
Xueniang.

843
00:38:15,310 --> 00:38:16,150
Trust me.

844
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:18,880
I'll soon smoothly send off the Duan family

845
00:38:18,910 --> 00:38:20,710
and then take you away from here.

846
00:38:21,030 --> 00:38:23,230
Let's go to a place where no one knows us

847
00:38:23,430 --> 00:38:24,590
and start over.

848
00:38:24,870 --> 00:38:26,600
Can there really be such a day?

849
00:38:27,390 --> 00:38:29,190
Although Uncle Cheng tried to stop me,

850
00:38:29,190 --> 00:38:32,070
I found nothing wrong with Madam.

851
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:35,150
We still can't relax our guard against the Sacred Blood Sect.

852
00:38:35,150 --> 00:38:38,480
This might be their plot to start internal strifes among us.

853
00:38:38,550 --> 00:38:39,350
I understand.

854
00:38:39,830 --> 00:38:41,120
Besides,

855
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:43,390
even if we can trust Gu Qingqiao temporarily,

856
00:38:43,390 --> 00:38:45,320
you shouldn't get too close to her.

857
00:38:46,230 --> 00:38:47,110
Brother.

858
00:38:47,430 --> 00:38:48,870
I can see clearly now.

859
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:51,830
You've grown deeply attached to Gu Qingqiao.

860
00:38:51,950 --> 00:38:52,750
And I

861
00:38:53,150 --> 00:38:56,230
absolutely won't allow you to be with the Star of Rebellion.

862
00:38:56,230 --> 00:38:58,840
Duan Yu, you are from the Duan family.

863
00:38:58,990 --> 00:39:01,260
You have the blood of the Duan family in your veins.

864
00:39:01,260 --> 00:39:04,030
The suitable woman for you must be someone of equal status.

865
00:39:04,030 --> 00:39:05,510
And her family can assist you.

866
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:06,670
Gu Qingqiao

867
00:39:06,990 --> 00:39:08,310
is not on the same path as you.

868
00:39:08,310 --> 00:39:10,720
I don't need a woman of equal status.

869
00:39:11,160 --> 00:39:13,590
I just want someone who shares mutual feelings with me.

870
00:39:13,590 --> 00:39:14,560
And that person

871
00:39:15,190 --> 00:39:16,440
is Gu Qingqiao.

872
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:18,590
Fine.

873
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:20,960
Let's not discuss how the Star of Rebellion

874
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:23,230
could endanger the Duan family.

875
00:39:23,660 --> 00:39:25,270
Just as you said today,

876
00:39:25,590 --> 00:39:28,030
Gu Qingqiao comes from another world.

877
00:39:28,150 --> 00:39:30,360
So even if we ultimately eliminate the Sacred Blood Sect,

878
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:31,550
resolve the crisis,

879
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:34,950
and help her gather the Four Treasures to open the gate of time and space.

880
00:39:34,950 --> 00:39:37,820
In the end, she will return to her own world.

881
00:39:38,830 --> 00:39:39,690
What about you?

882
00:39:40,220 --> 00:39:41,300
What will you do?

883
00:39:41,640 --> 00:39:42,520
If she leaves,

884
00:39:43,570 --> 00:39:45,090
I will remain unwed for life.
